content.rendered:
Directed by Mukesh Chhabra

Written by Shashank Khaitan, Suprotim Sengupta, Scott Neustadter, Michael H, Weber, John Green

Cast Sushant Singh Rajput (Immanuel Rajkumar Junior / Manny), Sanjana Sanghi (Kizie Basu), Sahil Vaid (Jagdish Pandey / JP), Saswata Chatterjee (Mr, Basu), Swastika Mukherjee (Mrs, Basu), Sunit Tandon (Dr, Jha), Saif Ali Khan (Abhimanyu Veer), Michael Muthu (Manny’s Father), Rajie Vijay Sarathi (Manny’s Mother), Subbalakshmi (Manny’s Nani (as Subhlaxmi)), Franaita Jijana (Foizey (as Franaita Jijina)), Durgesh Kumar (Rickshaw Puller), Salone Mehta (Mrs, Damaniya (Foizey’s Mother)), Anandita Sarkar (Mrs, D’Costa), Nimisha Dean (College Friend), Aftab (Rickshaw Goon), Sukhesh Arora (Singh), Azzy Bagria (Friend (as Bagria Azzy)), Shaji Dheeraj (College Friend), Driggu ((as Caio Sael)), Ritviq Joshi (Ghazal Singer),Mr, Karan, Kartik Kathiriya (Musician), Saurav Khurana (Patient), Milind Mehta (College Friend), Scott Milburn (Cancer Patient), Utsav Narula (Kizzies college friends), Saurabh Pal (Gazal Group), Jugal Popat (Omkar), Aditya Prakash (Son, Church Scene), Vikash Rajput (Singer (credit only)), Karan Sharma (Manny’s friend), Deependra Singh (Bengali), Samiran Singh (Singer), Manish Soni (Manny’s Frind)

Languages Hindi

Producers Prasanna R, Coondapur, Hetvi Karia, Rucha Pathak, Sanjeev Verma,

Production Fox STAR Studios
